# --- COPYRIGHT: never commit source books or any book-derived content ---
# The source PDFs and every ingested artefact (vault notes, extraction trees,
# envelopes, chunk/tag/artifact/xref records, run logs) contain VERBATIM
# copyrighted text. The whole of data/ is ignored so book text can never be
# swept in by `git add -A`. If a gold LABEL SHEET that is safe to commit is
# ever produced (chunk_ids + human labels ONLY, never full chunk_text), it
# must be un-ignored by its specific path below, e.g.:
#   !data/gold/labels.csv
data/
